These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
4 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, backgammon, billiard
City: miami, edinburgh, colone, prague
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, puzzles, video-games, fishing
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, bus, ship
 1. the person driving the bike is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is the person traveling to colone##1
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
 8. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to colone##5
 9. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
11. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Game          | billiard     | mah-jongg   | chess | backgammon |
| City   | edinburgh | miami    | prague   | colone    |
| Hobby           | video-games       | fishing   | puzzles   | singing     |
| Transport     | bike       | airplane | ship  | bus      |

