.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, bartender, scientist, nurse
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, orchid, begonia, zinnia
There 4 different types of food: carrot, plum, onion, garlic
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
 2. the person eating onion is in an odd position##4
 3. the person eating garlic is the engineer##1
 4. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 5. the scientist is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who growszinnia and the bartender##2
 8. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 9. the person eating plum is the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
11. the person driving the car is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Job      | bartender       | engineer | nurse     | scientist     |
| Flower   | orchid      | amaryllis       | zinnia | begonia |
| Food           | onion       | garlic    | plum     | carrot         |
| Transport     | skateboard | scooter     | car     | roller       |

