There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, water, iced-tea, tea
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 2. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 3. the coach is somewhere to the right of the dancer##5
 4. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
 5. the wooden house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 6. the person drinking tea is between the security-guard and the librarian##2
 7. the coach is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 8. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 9. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
10. the person drinking tea is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person drinking cola##1
12. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
