 3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the dutch##3
 4. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 5. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 6. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the fan of metal and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
 8. the malaysian is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
11. the fan of pop is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
13. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
