The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, reggae, classical, rock
4 different pets are kept: dog, cat, ferret, hedgehog
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, drama, epic
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the fan of rock##5
 2. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the owner of the dog is between the person playing scrabble and the owner of the hedgehog##2
 4. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
 5. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
 6. the person playing go is in an odd position##4
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
 8. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
 9. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
10. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
11. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
12. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Game      | go   | scrabble | billiard   | backgammon          |
| Music-Genre          | reggae    | rock        | classical     | ambient          |
| Pet           | cat | ferret        | dog | hedgehog |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | adventure     | drama      | disaster        |

