.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, water
City: london, san-francisco, rome, prague
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, october, june, january
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, hip-hop, trance, punk
 1. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 3. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person traveling to rome and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
 7. the person traveling to rome is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
10. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of punk##1
11. the fan of trance is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the fan of punk is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
13. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | water      | hot-chocolate | coffee     |
| City           | prague   | london  | san-francisco        | rome |
| Birthday   | april     | january     | june      | october   |
| Music-Genre     | hip-hop | trance | punk          | house     |

