.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, bird, chinchilla
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, social-worker, teacher
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, trike, scooter, taxi
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bongani, oliveros, ritmeester
 1. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
 2. the ritmeester-smoker is the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the davidoff-smoker##5
 4. the architect is in an even position##4
 5. the mechanic is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 6. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the bongani-smoker##5
 7. the social-worker is the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
 9. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
10. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
11. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
12. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Pet          | ferret | bird  | chinchilla    | guinea-pig       |
| Job           | mechanic  | teacher | social-worker | architect  |
| Transport   | trike    | scooter   | taxi  | bus     |
| Cigar   | ritmeester      | oliveros    | bongani        | davidoff |

 